      <h1 class="hero-title" style="color: #000;">What we stand for</h1>
      <p class="anonymous-ai-subheadline" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">At Hoogly, we believe that while the world of work has evolved, the human need for trust, psychological safety, and belonging remains constant.<br/><br/>
        That's why we stand for creating workplaces where every employee feels safe, valued, and connected—backed by science and research that shows how essential these elements are for well-being and performance.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

